JOHN R. VANCE v. ANN CLARK VANCE WHITE 32 So. (2nd) 606

June Term, 1947

November 18, 1947 Division B Rush & Pierce, George A. Pierce and Victor Blue, for appellant. Knight, Knight, Walrath & Pegues and Harry G. Kinkaid, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

Affirmed on authority of our opinion and judgment of Vance v. Vance, 143 Fla. 513, 197 So. 128.

So ordered.

THOMAS, C. J., BUFORD, ADAMS and BARNS, JJ., concur.
